T1  - An Operational Measure of Riskiness
AU  - Foster, Dean P.
AU  - Hart, Sergiu
Y1  - 2009/10/01
PY  - 2009
DA  - 2009/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.1086/644840
DO  - 10.1086/644840
T2  - Journal of Political Economy
JF  - Journal of Political Economy
SP  - 785
EP  - 814
VL  - 117
IS  - 5
PB  - The University of Chicago Press
N2  - We propose a measure of riskiness of ?gambles? (risky assets) that is objective: it depends only on the gamble and not on the decision maker. The measure is based on identifying for every gamble the critical wealth level below which it becomes ?risky? to accept the gamble.
AB  - We propose a measure of riskiness of ?gambles? (risky assets) that is objective: it depends only on the gamble and not on the decision maker. The measure is based on identifying for every gamble the critical wealth level below which it becomes ?risky? to accept the gamble.
SN  - 0022-3808
M3  - doi: 10.1086/644840
UR  - https://doi.org/10.1086/644840
Y2  - 2024/03/20
